.SS "7\&.2 User Check"
This feature checks for the existence of a user and the user’s group membership\&.
.SS "7\&.2\&.1 User Check Specific Keys"
Input keys are described in the table below:
.PP
Config Key TypeDescription userString Specifies the user name to check\&. This key is required\&. groupsCollection of Strings This is an optional key specifying a collection of groups the user should belong to\&. The user’s membership in each group will be checked\&.  
.SS "7\&.2\&.2 Output"
Output keys are described in the table below:
.PP
