Config Key TypeDescription os_versionsCollection of Strings A collection of strings corresponding to operating systems names, i\&.e\&. {“Ubuntu 16\&.04\&.3 LTS”, “Centos 7\&.4”, etc\&.}  kernel_versionsCollection of Strings A collection of strings corresponding to kernel version names, i\&.e\&. {“4\&.4\&.0-116-generic”, “4\&.13\&.0-36-generic”, etc\&.}  
