.SS "10\&.2 Output"
Module specific output keys are described in the table below: Output Key TypeDescription p2p_resultBool Indicates if the gpu and the specified peer have P2P capabilities\&. If this quantity is true, the GPU pair tested has p2p capabilities\&. If false, they are not peers\&. distanceInteger NUMA distance for these two peers hop_typeString Link type for each link hop (e\&.g\&., PCIe, HyperTransport, QPI, \&.\&.\&.) hop_distanceInteger NUMA distance for this particular hop transfer_idString String with format '<transfer_index>/<transfer_number>' where
.IP "\(bu" 2
